潛意識將「中國同香港係並列」呢個關係植入受眾腦入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a9c46caebc369f0c5fa21606c3a48603ad798a","tid":1491840,"uid":53683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:32:58.000Z","msg":"大家巴絲立場咁鮮明<br />\n我哋溝通就梗係可以第一句就黑警死全家<br />\n第二句就支那人冇一個係無辜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd05857570c1237d635895036416863b82a81ff","tid":1491840,"uid":53683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:42:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4db087ebb5b5d989b2f6ce672b5e9694630edaca","tid":1491840,"uid":53683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:50:22.000Z","msg":"突發<br />\n823要人！"},{"pid":"2227d0603342cd6fdb42ecd5a72ba140085a2475","tid":1491840,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac